width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/fOoFpRzpPo0itMZOS0nfBoGmHMJ.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/yPQK6EByZmDeAwR3ZaGPBOuW4K1.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":2283,"height":1284,"file_path":"/nFX1C3eSuRYko0aBTibEk2EZu6b.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-21T12:01:44.293+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Lust, Caution","runtime":158,"tagline":"To kill the enemy, she would have to capture his heart... and break her own.","homepage":"http://www.bvi.com.tw/movies/lust_caution/main.html","overview":"During World War II, a secret agent must seduce and assassinate an official who works for the Japanese puppet government in Shanghai."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Gefahr und Begierde","runtime":156,"tagline":"","homepage":"http://www.bvi.com.tw/movies/lust_caution/main.html","overview":"Drama von Regisseur Ang Lee, das 2007 beim Filmfest in Venedig als Bester Film ausgezeichnet wurde. China ist von Japan besetzt. Die Studentin Wang Jiahzi schließt sich einer militanten Widerstandsgruppe an, die einen hohen japanischen Beamten töten will. Um in seine Nähe zu kommen, nimmt sie eine andere Identität an, in der sie sich verliert."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"色‧戒","runtime":158,"tagline":"色易守，情难防","homepage":"","overview":"本是岭南大学学生的王佳芝（汤唯 饰）因战争辗转到了香港读书，她在香港大学加入了爱国青年邝裕民（王力宏 饰）组织的话剧组，他们主演的爱国话剧更激起了他们的爱国情操。当邝裕民得知汪伪政府的特务头子易先生（梁朝伟 饰）正在香港的时候，他们便密谋要刺杀易先生。化名“麦太太”的王佳芝很快得到了易太太（陈冲 饰）的信任与喜爱，同时美丽的“麦太太”也吸引了易先生的眼球，正当事情进行得如火如荼之际，易先生突然要回到上海去。  此后王佳芝一直生活在上海，没想到重遇了邝裕民。当得知刺杀行动还没结束时，王佳芝再次成为了特务，再次以“麦太太”的身份出现在易先生的面前。重逢后的二人关系进一步发展，此时的易先生因爱上了王佳芝而对她毫无忌讳，王佳芝的内心也变得起伏不定。刺杀行动进行正顺利，但当易先生送给王佳芝璀璨钻戒表达爱意时，王佳芝做出了惊人的决定……"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Dikkat Şehvet","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Asya sinemasının baş tacı olarak kabul edilen Tony Leung, karısının genç ve güzel arkadaşına aşık olan güçlü bir devlet adamıdır. Aralarında yaşanan ilişki, tutku dolu bir aşk ruletine dönüşür. Cinayet ise aşklarını kanıtlamanın tek yolu olacaktır."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Lust Caution","runtime":152,"tagline":"At dræbe fjenden, må hun fange hans hjerte... og knække sit eget.","homepage":"","overview":"2. verdenskrig truer og den unge kvindelige spion Wong Chia-Chi (Wang Tei) bliver sat til at udspionere den højtstående japanske minister Mr. Yee (Tony Leung). Under dække som Mrs. Mak forsøger hun at komme ind på livet af ham, men hurtigt erfarer hun, hvor svært det er at være intim med fjenden uden samtidig at involvere sig følelsesmæssigt."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Lust, Caution (Se jie) on vuonna 2007 julkaistu Ang Leen ohjaama yhteistuotantoelokuva. Amerikkalais-kiinalais-taiwanilais-hongkongilainen tuotanto on vakoilukertomus, jonka juonenkäänteet tapahtuvat Kiinassa toisen maailmansodan aikana.Elokuva palkittiin Venetsian elokuvajuhlilla Kultaisella leijonalla, ja se on ollut ehdolla myös Golden Globe -palkinnon saajaksi. Ang Lee teki jälleen yhteistyötä Hiipivä tiikeri, piilotettu lohikäärme -elokuvan kirjoittajien ja tuottajien kanssa."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"Lussuria - Seduzione e tradimento","runtime":157,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Film ambientato nella Shangai degli anni quaranta, occupata dai giapponesi, narra la storia di una studentessa arruolatasi in un gruppo di ragazzi universitari per mettere in atto un assassinio ai danni di un direttore del servizio segreto del governo fantoccio giapponese. Fingendosi una sofisticata signora diventerà l'amante del traditore, ma spingendosi sempre più oltre a questa relazione finirà per amarlo."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Lust, Caution","runtime":158,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Dans les années 1940, alors que le Japon occupe une partie de la Chine, la jeune étudiante Wong est chargée d'approcher et de séduire Mr Yee, un des chefs de la collaboration avec les Japonais, homme redoutable et méfiant que la Résistance veut supprimer. Très vite, la relation entre Wong et Mr Yee devient bien plus complexe que ne l'avait imaginé la jeune femme."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Touha, opatrnost","runtime":157,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Film se obrací do historie východní Asie a obsahuje akční sekvence, romantiku i erotiku. Odehrává se v Šanghaji během druhé světové války. Odbojová skupina naplánuje vraždu tamějšího bosse, japonského kolaboranta Yee, kterou má provést mladičká Wang Jiazhi. Jakmile se ale celý podnik rozjede, uskutečnit vraždu není tak snadné. Yee i Wang upadají do tajuplného vztahu, kde jeden nemůže mít druhého a přesto bez sebe nemohou být… V hlavních rolích se představí asijská superhvězda Tony Leung (Stvořeni pro lásku, Hard Boiled, Volavka ad.) a mladá čínská herečka a režisérka Tang Wei. Postavu manželky pana Yee ztvárnila čínská herečka a režisérka Joan Chen, kterou diváci znají z množství západních produkcí (např. Poslední císař)."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Deseo, peligro","runtime":0,"tagline":"Para matar al enemigo, ella tendría que conquistar su corazón... y romper el suyo propio.","homepage":"","overview":"Shanghai, 1942. La ciudad está ocupada por los japoneses. La señora Mak, una mujer rica y sofisticada, recuerda cómo empezó todo en 1938. Su verdadero nombre no es Mak, sino Wong Chia Chi. Poco antes de estallar la II Guerra Mundial (1939-1945), su padre huyó a Inglaterra y la dejó en China. Era estudiante universitaria y conoció a Kuang Yu Min, que acababa de fundar una compañía de teatro para fomentar el patriotismo. Wong Chia Chi se convirtió en la primera actriz de la compañía. Kuang, por su parte, convenció a un grupo de estudiantes para que asesinaran al señor Yee, un importante colaborador de los japoneses. Wong Chia Chi colaboró en el plan haciéndose pasar por la señora Mak: su cometido era hacerse amiga de la mujer de Yee para ganarse la confianza de éste y seducirlo. Todo iba sucediendo según lo previsto, hasta que se produjo un acontecimiento inesperado."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Вожделение","runtime":157,"tagline":"«To kill the enemy, she would have to capture his heart....and break her own.»","homepage":"","overview":"Шанхай. Вторая мировая война. Влиятельный политический деятель Мистер И безумно влюбляется в подругу своей молодой жены. Отношения их настолько нежны и трепетны, что обычно осторожный И даже не подозревает, что Ван — вовсе не та, за кого себя выдает! С каждым днем порочная связь заходит все дальше, а страсть становится все сильнее, и теперь уже невозможно остановиться…"},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Lust, Caution","runtime":152,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Tiden är 1942, platsen är ett ­Japan-ockuperat Shanghai, fulladdat med intrig och turbulens. Den mäktige Mr Yi som är en inflytelserik medlöpare på ockupationsmaktens sida blir en del av konspirationen som går ut på att oskadliggöra honom genom den unga, vackra aktivisten Wong."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Ellenséges vágyak","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Kína,1938. Wong igazi jó lány, aki épp most kezdi egyetemi tanulmányait. A fiatal nő teljesen magára maradt a világban, anyja meghalt, az apja pedig testvérével együtt Angliában rekedt a II. világháború kitörése miatt. Az egyetemen megtetszik neki egy diák, Kuang, miatta jelentkezik az iskolai drámacsoportba. A hazafias érzelmektől fűtött fiú veszélyes tervet eszel ki a japánokkal együttműködő kínaiak megbüntetésére: a magas beosztásban lévő Yee-t akarja megölni. Wongnak a színpad után, most az életben is szerepet kell játszani. Feladata, hogy Yee feleségének bizalmát elnyerve, a férfi szeretője legyen, előkészítve a terepet az ellenállók merényletének. Wong veszélyes játszmába kerül, szűz lányként egy csábító férjes asszonyt kell alakítania. Azzal pedig végképp nem számolt, hogy az ellenségétől függésbe kerül, a férfihez kötődő fizikai szenvedélye miatt."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"색, 계","runtime":158,"tagline":"다시, 사랑을 끝낸다","homepage":"","overview":"1938년 홍콩, 친일파의 핵심 인물이자 정보부 대장인 이(양조위)와 그를 암살하기 위해 막 부인으로 신분을 위장하고 접근하는 왕치아즈(탕웨이). 그녀의 임무는 자신의 신분을 위장하고 이의 아내(조안첸)에게 접근하여 신뢰를 쌓은 후 이에게 가까워 지는 것. 둘은 처음 본 순간부터 운명 같은 강렬한 이끌림을 느끼게 되지만 이의 상하이 발령으로 헤어지게 되고 암살 계획 또한 무산된다. 1941년 상하이, 다시 시작 된 암살계획으로 둘은 상하이에서 재회하게 된다. 경계를 푼 이, 그에게 다른 감정을 느끼는 왕치아즈. 이들은 서로에게 빠져들게 되는데..."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Se, Jie","runtime":157,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Tijdens de Tweede Wereldoorlog wordt het Chinese Shanghai bezet door Japan. Een groep jonge Chinezen maakt plannen om de collaborateur Mr. Yee te vermoorden. Leider Kuang geeft de mooie Wong de opdracht het vertrouwen van zijn vrouw te winnen en een affaire te beginnen met Yee."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Sedução, Conspiração","runtime":0,"tagline":"A armadilha está montada.","homepage":"","overview":"Thriller de espionagem passado durante a Segunda Guerra, em Xangai, que conta a história de uma jovem chamada Wang Jiazhi (Wei Tang), envolvida num perigoso jogo emocional e de intriga com o político Mr. Yee (Tony Leung Chiu Wai)."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"תשוקה, זהירות","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"הבמאי המהולל אנג לי,מציג מותחן ריגול מסוכן וחושני המתרחש על רקע השפע ובצל הסכנה,בשנחאי של תקופת מלחמת העולם השנייה השחקן האסיאתי טוני ליונג (\"גיבור\") מככב כדמות ממשלתית רבת עוצמה וכוח אשר נשבה בקסמיה של חברתה הצעירה של אשתו.אך וונג איננה באמת מי שהיא נראת.המשיכה ההדדית בין השניים הופכת לתשוקה מסחררת,וגורמת למשחק רולטה מסוכן של רגשות. שוב לא ניתן עוד להבדיל בין מסירות לבגידה,ורצח הופך למעשה האולטימטיבי של האהבה."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Προσοχή: Πόθος","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"'Η νεαρή Ουόνγκ, φοιτήτρια και ηθοποιός, εμπλέκεται με μια αντιστασιακή ομάδα που στόχο έχει να σκοτώσει τον Mr. Yee, τον Κινέζο αρχηγό της ασφάλειας, ο οποίος συνεργάζεται με τους Ιάπωνες. Προσεγγίζει τη γυναίκα του και γίνεται η καλύτερή της φίλη έχοντας απώτατο στόχο να παρασύρει τον σύζυγό της σε μια ερωτική περιπέτεια. Το σχέδιο προχωρά όπως το είχε καταστρώσει, μέχρι τη στιγμή που αρχίζει να συνειδητοποιεί πως ο στόχος και τα συναισθήματά της βρίσκονται σε πάλη…"},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"ラスト、コーション","runtime":0,"tagline":"その愛は、許されるのか？","homepage":"","overview":"1938年、日中戦争の激化によって中国本土から香港に逃れていた女子大学生・王佳芝（ワン・チアチー）は、学友・鄺祐民（クァン・ユイミン）の勧誘で抗日運動をかかげる学生劇団に入団。翌年、佳芝も地下工作員として、暗殺の機を窺うため特務機関の易（イー）を誘惑したが、易の厳しい警戒で暗殺は未遂に終わる。3年後、再度、易暗殺の工作員として抜擢された佳芝は激しい性愛を交わすうち、すさまじい孤独の苦悩を抱える易にいつしか魅かれてゆく。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"شهوت، احتیاط","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"Ostrożnie, pożądanie","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Szanghaj lat 40. pod japońską okupacją. Członkowie podziemnego ruchu oporu, planując dokonać zamachu na ważnej figurze z kolaboracyjnego rządu, wysyłają dziewczynę, która ma go uwieść."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"色，戒","runtime":0,"tagline":"［殺一個該殺的人 很難］［ 救一個不該救的人 更難］［愛一個不該愛的人 難上加難］情慾 佈下了命運的局...","homepage":"","overview":"一個噯昧的年代，政治上是非黑白顛倒，感情也可變得真假難分。王佳芝與易先生活於汪精衞的偽政府年代，女的是愛國份子，男的是特務頭目。一切快要分崩離析，王佳芝受愛國組織之命，暗殺特務易先生。易先生挑通眼眉，唯獨天生好色。色誘行動順理成章地展開，暗殺行動卻又終告失敗，但王佳芝與易先生的私情，又豈可就此告吹？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Порочний зв'язок","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Шанхай. Друга світова війна. Впливовий політичний діяч Містер Йі шалено закохується в подругу своєї молодої дружини. Стосунки їх настільки ніжні і трепетні, що зазвичай обережний Йі навіть не підозрює, що Ванг — зовсім не та, за кого себе видає! З кожним днем порочний зв'язок заходить все далі, а пристрасть стає все сильнішою, і тепер уже неможливо зупинитися..."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Geismas, įspėjimas","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Jis išdėlioja jausmų, išdavysčių, šantažo ir geismo labirintą tarp Honkongo ir Šanchajaus. Graži ir geraširdė Wang (akt. Tang Wei) neteko abiejų tėvų dėl karo. Jos mama tragiškai žuvo, o tėtis - pabėgo iš gimtinės ir dingo be žinios kažkur Anglijoje. Susižavėjusi pasitikinčiu savimi aktyvistu mergina savanoriškai įstoja į pogrindinio teatro trupę. Aktoriais apsimetantys jaunuoliai tik dėl akių vaidina spektakliuose, o visą likusį laiką skirią slaptojo pasipriešinimo organizavimui. Jie seka išdavikišką veiklą vykdančius politikus, renka kompromituojančią medžiagą ir rengia pasikėsinimo planus. Wang gauna pavojingą užduotį, kuri kardinaliai pakeis jos gyvenimą. Drovi mergina stengsis sugundyti itin aukštas pareigas užimantį Kinijos vyriausybės pareigūną Yee, užsitarnauti besąlygišką jo pasitikėjimą ir tapti jo meiluže."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"Desejo e Perigo","runtime":158,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Durante a Segunda Guerra Mundial, uma agente secreta deve seduzir e assassinar um oficial que trabalha para o governo fantoche japonês em Xangai."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Lust, Caution","runtime":151,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En ung kvinne blir dratt inn i et farlig politisk spill med erotiske elementer for å blottstille en mektig politiker som er medløper for de japanske invasjonsstyrkene i Shangai. Spørsmålet er hvem av dem som vil bøte med livet."},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"色，戒","runtime":157,"tagline":"色易守，情難防","homepage":"","overview":"抗戰時期，女大學生王佳芝欲施美人計，刺殺汪精衛身邊的大紅人易先生。當佳芝成功勾引易先生準備下手時，卻發現自己對他動了真情…"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Sắc, Giới","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Sắc giới có lẽ là bộ phim gây nhiều tranh cãi nhất của đạo diễn Lý An trong suốt sự nghiệp đạo diễn của ông , người ta không phải tranh cãi về hàng loạt giải thưởng lớn mà phim đạt được tại nhiều liên hoan phim khác nhau mà là về một câu trả lời chưa được giải đáp “Cảnh nóng trong phim là thật hay chỉ là dàn dựng?”. Những người trong cuộc không phủ nhận cũng không xác thực làm cho nhiều người lại càng tò mò và cho dù câu trả lời là như thế nào thì cũng phải nói rằng nội dung của phim rất hay."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"ვნება","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"სიუჟეტი ვითარდება შანხაიში. მეორე მსოფლიო ომის პერიოდში. გავლენიან პოლიტიკურ მოღვაწეს მისტერ იის თავდავიწყებით შეუყვერდა თავისი ახალგაზრდა ცოლის დაქალი. მათი ურთიერთობა იმდენად ნაზი და მთრთოლვარეა, რომ ჩვეულებრივ ძალიან ფრთხილი იი, ვერც კი წარმოიდგენს, რომ ვანგი სულ სხვა ადამიანია!"},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"เล่ห์ราคะ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Desig, perill","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Durant la Segona Guerra Mundial, una agent secreta ha de seduir i després assassinar un funcionari que treballa per al govern titella japonès a Xangai. La seva missió s’enterboleix quan es s’enamora de l'home que té l’encàrrec de matar."},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"},{"data":{"title":"Luxură, precauție","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":91073,"adult":false,"title":"Late Autumn","video":false,"overview":"Anna learns in prison that her mother has passed away in Seattle. Prison officials grants Anna a three day furlough to attend her mother's funeral. Anna embarks on a long trip to Seattle. Hoon is a Korean immigrant who works as a gigolo. Hoon is now on the run from a wealthy client's furious husband. These two seemingly lost souls are about to share three memorable days together.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7591,"vote_count":71,"poster_path":"/4SNjM2dUrq21TPK2faONOQ8riav.jpg","release_date":"2011-02-17","vote_average":6.746,"backdrop_path":"/qFChVlWuERqGVXuvjfoZcbj2t0k.jpg","original_title":"만추","original_language":"ko"},{"id":10451,"adult":false,"title":"Eat Drink Man Woman","video":false,"overview":"Retired and widowed Chinese master chef Chu lives in modern day Taipei, with his three attractive daughters, all of whom are unattached. Soon, each daughter encounters a new man in their lives. When these new relationships blossom, stereotypes are broken and the living situation within the family changes.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.7357,"vote_count":389,"poster_path":"/olhIWtIBFg6VWK59DEd4lAvgVgz.jpg","release_date":"1994-08-03","vote_average":7.634,"backdrop_path":"/tllmUjmEQKF0OaH7FgqZYnLBsYB.jpg","original_title":"飲食男女","original_language":"zh"},{"id":45380,"adult":false,"title":"Crazy Stone","video":false,"overview":"Three thieves try to steal a valuable jade that is tightly guarded by a security chief. But the security guards are not the only obstacle these thieves are facing. An extremely unlucky internationally known master thief is also trying to get a hand on this piece of precious jade. What would be the final destination of this piece of crazy stone?","genre_ids":[28,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9855,"vote_count":139,"poster_path":"/4NVNv2sQKZKb1HtGExUqp3Ukd7f.jpg","release_date":"2006-06-30","vote_average":7.612,"backdrop_path":"/8xzVdkNPNbqT6kJA6IHaRKFpt0B.jpg","original_title":"疯狂的石头","original_language":"zh"},{"id":30112,"adult":false,"title":"Lost in Beijing","video":false,"overview":"A look at modern-day life in China's capital centered on a ménage-a-quatre involving a young woman, her boss, her husband and her boss's wife.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":15.8946,"vote_count":61,"poster_path":"/2LZ7qbdnCqlOzlngcj5wdvnLfjA.jpg","release_date":"2007-09-26","vote_average":6.541,"backdrop_path":"/7F1djgcBJkMWFOeQ0ZK4b5Q3LPb.jpg","original_title":"苹果","original_language":"zh"},{"id":25626,"adult":false,"title":"The Founding of a Republic","video":false,"overview":"The tale of one man who fought against the tyranny of a ruler and led his people in battle in the ultimate sacrifice for his country.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.5683,"vote_count":64,"poster_path":"/fqLl0KQzj74yx1QQ1gyrpqjOhJh.jpg","release_date":"2009-09-17","vote_average":5.2,"backdrop_path":"/A1gDvcNGFkXg57nLuh5Hk2E8B5w.jpg","original_title":"建国大业","original_language":"zh"},{"id":571687,"adult":false,"title":"A Perfectly Normal Family","video":false,"overview":"Emma has a perfectly normal family until one day it turns out her dad, Thomas, is transgender. As Thomas becomes Agnete, both father and daughter struggle to hold on to what they had while accepting that everything has changed.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3232,"vote_count":48,"poster_path":"/qSChbRNvhpz6LOPxvTFuIyeOPTd.jpg","release_date":"2020-02-20","vote_average":6.604,"backdrop_path":"/bJ6ASfW8ai55zISPSgRQCDdctjO.jpg","original_title":"En helt almindelig familie","original_language":"da"},{"id":55717,"adult":false,"title":"The Wind Blows Round","video":false,"overview":"The aging, conservative population of a small, sleepy village in the Italian Alps are surprised to see that a former French professor has settled there with his young wife and their three children to produce goat cheese, in order to escape the wrongs of civilization. At first they are suspicious of his unconventional ideas and lifestyle, then are conquered by the enthusiasm, kindness, helpfulness of the young family and start to see in them a possible rebirth of the place. But little by little misunderstandings, envy and conflicts take over.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1972,"vote_count":39,"poster_path":"/owmpPRk0ek3F7Omt67kVli7EC21.jpg","release_date":"2006-06-05","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/A2n2sPX8WArWVjaBV101EsGSOAH.jpg","original_title":"Il Vento Fa Il Suo Giro","original_language":"it"},{"id":57310,"adult":false,"title":"The Sunday Woman","video":false,"overview":"Police commissioner Santamaria is investigating the murder of the ambiguous architect Mr. Garrone. The investigations soon drive him into the Torino's high society. Santamaria suspect Anna Carla and at the same time falls in love for her. Lello is the lover of Massimo, Anna Carla’s gay friend. He is following another direction in order to find out the truth, and his results are confusing the Policeman. But another murder happens...","genre_ids":[80,9648,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6269,"vote_count":78,"poster_path":"/jb2Ocf9vNJUoM4JoISUIkxtGEDK.jpg","release_date":"1975-12-23","vote_average":6.41,"backdrop_path":"/54upLqnMOkkmsh8KC1WirJrar0B.jpg","original_title":"La donna della domenica","original_language":"it"},{"id":41003,"adult":false,"title":"White Palace","video":false,"overview":"Max Baron is a Jewish advertising executive in his 20s who's still getting over the death of his wife. Nora Baker is a 40-something diner waitress who enjoys the wilder side of life. Mismatched or not, their attraction is instant and smoldering. With time, however, their class and age differences become an obstacle in their relationship, especially since Max can't keep Nora a secret from his Jewish friends and upper-crust associates forever.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.8509,"vote_count":180,"poster_path":"/nUxEeMzDNIrxlUXTmg3ApKj4EhU.jpg","release_date":"1990-10-19","vote_average":6.372,"backdrop_path":"/yme0UvacQuWaZK9QiywD6lvx0Oz.jpg","original_title":"White Palace","original_language":"en"},{"id":37557,"adult":false,"title":"Shanghai Triad","video":false,"overview":"Shanghai, China, 1930. When young Shuisheng arrives from the countryside, his uncle Liushu puts him at the service of Bijou, the mistress of Laoda, supreme boss of the Tang Triad, constantly threatened by his enemies, both those he knows and those lurking in the shadows.","genre_ids":[18,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.931,"vote_count":105,"poster_path":"/tzG1UxUSfPACREjgBrsPDRUvneH.jpg","release_date":"1995-09-14","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/gHG1OogmvDJldyi1tjqncjoblKV.jpg","original_title":"摇啊摇，摇到外婆桥","original_language":"zh"},{"id":64631,"adult":false,"title":"David's Birthday","video":false,"overview":"Two couples are enjoying their summer at the beach, but when the grown son of one couple arrives, it surprisingly stirs something in the husband of the other couple, will the forbidden feelings end badly?","genre_ids":[9648,18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.406,"vote_count":58,"poster_path":"/4PhnXpYe0BS2vE0AwpYUUVRsLG6.jpg","release_date":"2009-09-08","vote_average":5.6,"backdrop_path":"/nKn5mUGugWunPptdXvrAh5GNo2e.jpg","original_title":"Il compleanno","original_language":"it"},{"id":477359,"adult":false,"title":"Beyond Brotherhood","video":false,"overview":"Two young siblings ended up living on the streets, having nothing left but their love. It's a story about survival, second chances and second falls, with an unexpected turn at the end.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3079,"vote_count":31,"poster_path":"/tExuJbpB9vDdpFK31QEBq4aksPn.jpg","release_date":"2017-08-17","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":"/9LEVhjQVUrhgOmlI3BP75aZhcqs.jpg","original_title":"Más que hermanos","original_language":"es"},{"id":16447,"adult":false,"title":"Woman Is the Future of Man","video":false,"overview":"As the first snow falls in Seoul, two old friends reunite; one is a successful college professor, and the other, a struggling filmmaker recently returned from the United States. After their reminiscences, they finally decide to go in search of the young woman each had romanced years earlier.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8362,"vote_count":63,"poster_path":"/3bovtjGw5XB3aDKaWkfYnCupBbI.jpg","release_date":"2004-05-05","vote_average":6.127,"backdrop_path":"/5HUWQDUJMIL4Di2C5TC2eU6f7tU.jpg","original_title":"여자는 남자의 미래다","original_language":"ko"},{"id":96010,"adult":false,"title":"The Way I Spent the End of the World","video":false,"overview":"Bucharest 1989 - the last year of Ceausecu's dictatorship. Eva lives with her parents and her 7 year old brother, Lalalilu. One day at school, Eva and her boyfriend accidentally break a bust of Ceausescu. They are forced to confess their crime before a disciplinary committee and Eva is expelled from school and transferred to a reformatory establishment. There she meets Andrei, and decides to escape Romania with him. Lalalilu becomes convinced that Ceausescu is the main reason for Eva's decision to leave. So with his friends from school he devises a plan to kill the dictator.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5543,"vote_count":33,"poster_path":"/gIjQQ7XR2CBB58XSmmYeH2G0fFg.jpg","release_date":"2006-09-15","vote_average":5.879,"backdrop_path":"/p4qsVHxf7gtsxnqdBjID0ZxN9s1.jpg","original_title":"Cum mi-am petrecut sfârșitul lumii","original_language":"ro"},{"id":254679,"adult":false,"title":"The Little House","video":false,"overview":"Following the death of the unmarried and childless Taki, Takeshi, a young relative of hers, discovers several pages of closely written lines in which the old lady has recorded her memories. This is how he learns the truth about her youth working as a housemaid and nanny for the Hirai family in a little house in Tokyo with a red gabled roof.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7978,"vote_count":45,"poster_path":"/hfi1kRQv3kf6Ws8kxJ5jWM8vFvJ.jpg","release_date":"2014-01-25","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/d7DiWzIbyhorVdFpIszjXkWXmR8.jpg","original_title":"小さいおうち","original_language":"ja"},{"id":80212,"adult":false,"title":"Make Up","video":false,"overview":"Being a mortuary cosmetologist, Min-Hsiu is used to seeing dead bodies until she accidentally spots a female corpse – her high school teacher Miss Chen Ting. Nie Cheng-Fu, Chen Ting’s husband, loves his wife profoundly and tries to find more memories of her with Min-Hsiu’s help. At that point, a detective, Kuo Yung-Ming, senses that the truth behind this case may not be as simple as it seems. Death is not the end of  life, but another beginning of it...","genre_ids":[14,18,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.267,"vote_count":14,"poster_path":"/diMS7400FWFq1lGyuKbwfdtVbKd.jpg","release_date":"2011-05-13","vote_average":3.9,"backdrop_path":"/iih77ROvNC8iMgW5sEJfjGwea3X.jpg","original_title":"命運化妝師","original_language":"zh"},{"id":28564,"adult":false,"title":"Manhattan Melodrama","video":false,"overview":"The friendship between two orphans endures even though they grow up on opposite sides of the law and fall in love with the same woman.","genre_ids":[80,18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5957,"vote_count":77,"poster_path":"/gAuBeXANJ0NhlQY7kmas63dFMz7.jpg","release_date":"1934-05-04","vote_average":6.961,"backdrop_path":"/eIMOU6rAceFLx37oeJn3Tqh5R2e.jpg","original_title":"Manhattan Melodrama","original_language":"en"},{"id":313452,"adult":false,"title":"Love On The Cloud","video":false,"overview":"Romance gets complicated in modern-day Beijing.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0064,"vote_count":15,"poster_path":"/wf50DWkxOuOThfY2rcgnR3ym0DP.jpg","release_date":"2014-12-24","vote_average":3.733,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"微爱之渐入佳境","original_language":"zh"},{"id":83446,"adult":false,"title":"Oblomov","video":false,"overview":"St. Petersburg, mid 19th century: the indolent, middle-aged Oblomov lives in a flat with his older servant, Zakhar. He sleeps much of the day, dreaming of his childhood on his parents' estate. His boyhood companion, Stoltz, now an energetic and successful businessman, adds Oblomov to his circle whenever he's in the city, and Oblomov's life changes when Stoltz introduces him to Olga, lovely and cultured. When Stoltz leaves for several months, Oblomov takes a country house near Olga's, and she determines to change him: to turn him into a man of society, action, and culture. Soon, Olga and Oblomov are in love; but where, in the triangle, does that leave Stoltz?","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5992,"vote_count":44,"poster_path":"/ero51WWvP9UJXPMnH3DyZLjIofR.jpg","release_date":"1980-04-01","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/gwRS8rZMGLMhjauNZpoHJ9FI8Zt.jpg","original_title":"Несколько дней из жизни И.И. Обломова","original_language":"ru"},{"id":8447,"adult":false,"title":"Angels and Insects","video":false,"overview":"In Victorian England, wealthy patriarch Sir Harald Alabaster invites an impoverished biologist, William Adamson, into his home. There, William tries to continue his work, but is distracted by Alabaster's seductive daughter, Eugenia. William and Eugenia begin a torrid romance, but as the couple become closer, the young scientist begins to realize that dark, disturbing things are happening behind the closed doors of the Alabaster manor.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7323,"vote_count":56,"poster_path":"/w1i5JdddoLuzSmnKo5ORDoKdMm2.jpg","release_date":"1995-09-10","vote_average":6.134,"backdrop_path":"/h5PrPi1fnGACJiYoIJxBpAkqhGU.jpg","original_title":"Angels and Insects","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":179,"adult":false,"title":"The Interpreter","video":false,"overview":"After Silvia Broome, an interpreter at United Nations headquarters, overhears plans of an assassination, an American Secret Service agent is sent to investigate.","genre_ids":[80,53],"popularity":2.4155,"vote_count":1531,"poster_path":"/wTidq3J9fh8sEOAlD8WZFHVLSuB.jpg","release_date":"2005-04-08","vote_average":6.309,"backdrop_path":"/A5mBIAtZOqVpAVUXolwtOnaQcZc.jpg","original_title":"The Interpreter","original_language":"en"},{"id":195,"adult":false,"title":"Trouble in Paradise","video":false,"overview":"Thief Gaston Monescu and pickpocket Lily are partners in crime and love. Working for perfume company executive Mariette Colet, the two crooks decide to combine their criminal talents to rob their employer. Under the alias of Monsieur Laval, Gaston uses his position as Mariette's personal secretary to become closer to her. However, he takes things too far when he actually falls in love with Mariette, and has to choose between her and Lily.","genre_ids":[35,80,10749],"popularity":0.6605,"vote_count":301,"poster_path":"/FBxuoLRD3Biyul14unT5m3PYNS.jpg","release_date":"1932-10-30","vote_average":7.41,"backdrop_path":"/8xFIubJoxyidKaGjO1dc0btC9e7.jpg","original_title":"Trouble in Paradise","original_language":"en"},{"id":198,"adult":false,"title":"To Be or Not to Be","video":false,"overview":"During the Nazi occupation of Poland, an acting troupe becomes embroiled in a Polish soldier's efforts to track down a German spy.","genre_ids":[35,10752,10749],"popularity":1.1512,"vote_count":809,"poster_path":"/dDQRpEoyjHT4fzw9cNklIvZuXYg.jpg","release_date":"1942-03-06","vote_average":7.8,"backdrop_path":"/28vvMlh490bxipmhkbYTQissiof.jpg","original_title":"To Be or Not to Be","original_language":"en"},{"id":247136,"adult":false,"title":"The Temptation of Kimono","video":false,"overview":"Mikage will get married to Youiti next year, she agrees to live with Youiti's parents. One day, Youiti's father disrobed Mikage's Kimono and raped her. To her astonishment, her fiancé Youiti whom Mikage considers true love has an affair with his young stepmother. Shocked and devastated, what will Mikage do?","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":1.4753,"vote_count":21,"poster_path":"/2oVfD5rUV2EElbQ11ds2Vf5nRaZ.jpg","release_date":"2009-03-27","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"M家の新妻 変態洗礼","original_language":"ja"},{"id":203,"adult":false,"title":"Mean Streets","video":false,"overview":"A small-time hood must choose from among love, friendship and the chance to rise within the mob.","genre_ids":[18,80],"popularity":2.4202,"vote_count":2251,"poster_path":"/9msfwOeGc9uL1iRRTBdEf15XonC.jpg","release_date":"1973-10-14","vote_average":7.058,"backdrop_path":"/qdecDSIVoqctIoYoOhLH3TgSYLD.jpg","original_title":"Mean Streets","original_language":"en"},{"id":418970,"adult":false,"title":"Just to Be Sure","video":false,"overview":"Erwan, a strapping Breton who clears mines for a living, is shaken when he discovers that his father is not his father. Despite his affection for the man who raised him, he quietly sets out to find his biological father, and succeeds in locating Joseph, an endearing old codger he takes a liking to. Just when things look settled, another unexpected “bomb” hits Erwan in the form of Anna, an elusive nymph.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":0.6197,"vote_count":213,"poster_path":"/xlnf99tJK93J1G9LlihOxdnWJoZ.jpg","release_date":"2017-09-06","vote_average":6.397,"backdrop_path":"/588O5O6C0Wq8RfIctuthalUkW3n.jpg","original_title":"Ôtez-moi d'un doute","original_language":"fr"},{"id":947752,"adult":false,"title":"El Fidayoune","video":false,"overview":"In the midst of the Algerian War in 1957, fighters (fidayounes) resisted French intervention with the help of a doctor.","genre_ids":[18,10752],"popularity":0.1148,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/tgi0r1ihDmLw0lnmQK1PxyZaeZ6.jpg","release_date":"1971-01-01","vote_average":10,"backdrop_path":"/lgRJIVzzJAkRgIKn2PI9DKnmici.jpg","original_title":"El Fidayoune","original_language":"ar"},{"id":246942,"adult":false,"title":"The Fox Lover","video":false,"overview":"When the white fox spirit falls for a naïve mortal girl, his loyalties are tested in the clash between humans and demons.","genre_ids":[14,10749,28],"popularity":0.7929,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/33shJRMsAsAhu5ZPRVQpd8pCnga.jpg","release_date":"2013-09-27","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/dOdP0mZH4Zf0s6qjZfKoxnz3DGw.jpg","original_title":"白狐","original_language":"zh"},{"id":659,"adult":false,"title":"The Tin Drum","video":false,"overview":"In 1924, Oskar Matzerath is born in the Free City of Danzig. At age three, he falls down a flight of stairs and stops growing. In 1939, World War II breaks out.","genre_ids":[18,36,10752],"popularity":4.8692,"vote_count":518,"poster_path":"/tm408GMyQqfqFJ7MKCkwc5uQ3wi.jpg","release_date":"1979-05-02","vote_average":6.94,"backdrop_path":"/uZJjc4hMgckb3H3tVkTmbmcBhIT.jpg","original_title":"Die Blechtrommel","original_language":"de"},{"id":661,"adult":false,"title":"The Marriage of Maria Braun","video":false,"overview":"Maria marries a young soldier in the last days of World War II, only for him to go missing in the war. She must rely on her beauty and ambition to navigate the difficult post-war years alone.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.6702,"vote_count":293,"poster_path":"/tXjZEzlf4WQwZ4Dt53gXeJVuO7p.jpg","release_date":"1979-03-23","vote_average":7.353,"backdrop_path":"/ejp6CZQ64mEvewfit2fSIpOYxGR.jpg","original_title":"Die Ehe der Maria Braun","original_language":"de"},{"id":665,"adult":false,"title":"Ben-Hur","video":false,"overview":"In 26 AD, Judah Ben-Hur, a Jew in ancient Judea, opposes the occupying Roman empire.  Falsely accused by a Roman childhood friend-turned-overlord of trying to kill the Roman governor, he is put into slavery and his mother and sister are taken away as prisoners.","genre_ids":[36,18,12],"popularity":8.8819,"vote_count":3042,"poster_path":"/m4WQ1dBIrEIHZNCoAjdpxwSKWyH.jpg","release_date":"1959-11-18","vote_average":7.883,"backdrop_path":"/sU3gFo7Gn67zjtKXIvzJ4omcUbH.jpg","original_title":"Ben-Hur","original_language":"en"},{"id":668,"adult":false,"title":"On Her Majesty's Secret Service","video":false,"overview":"With the help of Marc-Ange Draco, head of the Unione Corse crime syndicate, and Draco's troubled daughter Tracy, James Bond tracks his archnemesis, Ernst Stravro Blofeld, to a mountaintop retreat in the Swiss Alps, where he is training an army of beautiful, lethal women.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":5.3271,"vote_count":2077,"poster_path":"/m3KfbxvqaiAvRJ6MpguA3GuLdDQ.jpg","release_date":"1969-12-18","vote_average":6.562,"backdrop_path":"/58pMrmwwcKamJIdjUlinE6QX1Fs.jpg","original_title":"On Her Majesty's Secret Service","original_language":"en"},{"id":682,"adult":false,"title":"The Man with the Golden Gun","video":false,"overview":"Cool government operative James Bond searches for a stolen invention that can turn the sun's heat into a destructive weapon. He soon crosses paths with the menacing Francisco Scaramanga, a hitman so skilled he has a seven-figure working fee. Bond then joins forces with the swimsuit-clad Mary Goodnight, and together they track Scaramanga to a Thai tropical isle hideout where the killer-for-hire lures the slick spy into a deadly maze for a final duel.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":4.9709,"vote_count":2220,"poster_path":"/xVkbKwGnBVNQ122GN5bCTMyPbWz.jpg","release_date":"1974-12-04","vote_average":6.456,"backdrop_path":"/3tpNEbRahT8smy7RraaWa0xg9Gv.jpg","original_title":"The Man with the Golden Gun","original_language":"en"},{"id":688,"adult":false,"title":"The Bridges of Madison County","video":false,"overview":"Photographer Robert Kincaid wanders into the life of housewife Francesca Johnson for four days in the 1960s.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":2.8167,"vote_count":2320,"poster_path":"/aCBrhOQjhG397GLkEZ49zReQEKX.jpg","release_date":"1995-06-02","vote_average":7.704,"backdrop_path":"/4TnGcUsyd6ixuLWHaaEG5BGkAIp.jpg","original_title":"The Bridges of Madison County","original_language":"en"},{"id":695,"adult":false,"title":"Short Cuts","video":false,"overview":"Many loosely connected characters cross paths in this film, based on the stories of Raymond Carver. Waitress Doreen Piggot accidentally runs into a boy with her car. Soon after walking away, the child lapses into a coma. While at the hospital, the boy's grandfather tells his son, Howard, about his past affairs. Meanwhile, a baker starts harassing the family when they fail to pick up the boy's birthday cake.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":1.5844,"vote_count":660,"poster_path":"/nAEBc3g9bHAcF9whKFMfIxHxVwn.jpg","release_date":"1993-10-01","vote_average":7.195,"backdrop_path":"/a0OjGWE9ru1OlKLBujbz3mAYYxU.jpg","original_title":"Short Cuts","original_language":"en"},{"id":696,"adult":false,"title":"Manhattan","video":false,"overview":"Manhattan explores how the life of a middle-aged television writer dating a teenage girl is further co